      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "A deep navy blue like #000080 is a great choice for a banking app, it's professional and trustworthy. You can consider the following colors as complements or analogous to #000080: \n\nFor complements, a light gray or beige (#F7F7F7 or #F5F5DC) can create a nice contrast and add a sense of balance to your design. A warm, muted gold (#FFD700) can also add a touch of sophistication and luxury.\n\nFor analogous colors, a blue-green (#0097A7) or a dark gray-blue (#333399) can create a cohesive and calming palette. A soft, creamy white (#FFFFFF or #FFFFFFCC) can also help to soften the dark navy blue and add some visual breathing room.\n\nYou can also experiment with different shades and tints of blue to find the perfect balance for your design.",
