      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That gold looks okay, but maybe a bit too \"bright\" for a bank? Can you give me some more specific accent color options? Maybe something a bit more unique or \"characterful\" but still keeping that high-end corporate feel. Do you have any specific palettes that stand out?",
